<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="Q" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Quietly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Quietly,</orth> 1) still, without motion: <cit><quote>lie q.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 709" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 709</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) without disturbance or alarm, peaceably: <cit><quote>so shall you q. enjoy your hope,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.138" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 138</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.153" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 153</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.153" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 153</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 2, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.4.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 4, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.5.44" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.4.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 4, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 4.2.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 2, 29</bibl>.
<lb />3) calmly: <cit><quote>these quarrels must be q. debated,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 3, 20</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>